{"word":"καθάπτω","slug":"καθάπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαϑάπτω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἅπτω\">ἅπτω</a></el>; ‘fasten’] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> sense ‘take a firm hold’, <b>fasten:</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχιδνα\">ἔχιδνα</a> ϰαϑῆψεν τῆς χειρὸς <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:αὐτοῦ\">αὐτοῦ</a></el> a snake fastened itself on his hand <b><a href='B:510 28:3'>Ac 28:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καθάπερ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καθαριεῖ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}